The holiday season may have come and gone but its memories may linger in the minds of guests and visitors who had a firsthand experience of exceptional hospitality at the IBOM ICON Hotel and Golf Resort. The Christmas season offered the hotel another opportunity to reiterate its commitment to providing a truly world-class hospitality experience for guests. From the hotel’s ambience, culinary delight, family picnics, excursions, live band performances, fun activities for kids and various outdoor sports, no stone was left unturned to provide the desired atmosphere of merriment for the Christmas season. These efforts surely have not gone unnoticed as guests commended the new management of the hotel, ICON Hotels and Resorts Nigeria for the noticeable improvements observed. For Otobong Attah, a guest at the IBOM ICON Hotels and Golf Resort, the hotel is a lovely resort and a nice get away destination for the holidays. “It has a welcoming ambience, serene next-to-nature type of resort. There is a great restaurant, swimming pool, a golf course and lots of activities to do. Very family friendly!” he stated Another guest, Abasibiangake Akpabio commended the management of the hotel – ICON Hotels and Resorts Nigeria. “They have maintained the record of excellent hospitality services. During the Yuletide, the hotel offered an amazing Christmas promo package in the spirit of the season,” he noted. ICON Hotels and Resorts Nigeria’s Managing Director, Mr. Adetope Kayode appreciated the highly esteemed customers of the Hotel, who through their patronage and positive reviews have ensured that IBOM ICON Hotel and Golf Resort remains a choice destination for hospitality. 